Setup:
Put on a PHP Server with this file/folder structure:
 - pages (this is where the old pages stay) [read permissions required from linker.php]
 - newpages (this is where the new pages will stay after linker is ran) [write premissions required from linker.php]

Variables:
	$max - how many links to generate from the first
	$folder - the folder of the old pages
	$newfolder - the folder where the newly generated files will be put
